      "raw_text": "Beginning Sunday, June 10, the\nNorthern Pacific will inaugurate their\nSunday excursions to Occur d'Alene\nCity and st. Maries. Sunday train\nwill leave at a. m, returning to\nSpokane at Z p. m. The steamer\nGeorge Cakes, the largest and most\ncommodious steamer on the lake. will\nmake the trip Occur dAlene to Har-\nrison, Chatcalet and st. Maries and\nreturn, connecting with train both\nways; fare for the entire round trip\n$3.50. Finest trip for a days ride to\nbe found.\n\n\n]. w. HILL, General Agent."
